{
  "chapter": "013",
  "title": "三代世表",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "太史公论三代之记",
      "text": ""
    },
    "1.1": {
      "title": "三代之记由来已久",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">五帝</span>、<span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">三代</span>的记载，由来已久。"
    },
    "1.2": {
      "title": "殷以前诸侯难谱",
      "text": "从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>代以前，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>的世系无法编成谱牒，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>代以来才略可记述。"
    },
    "1.3": {
      "title": "孔子作春秋",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>依据史官的文书编次<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">春秋</span>，记载<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，订正时节和<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">日月</span>，可谓详尽了。"
    },
    "1.4": {
      "title": "尚书缺年月",
      "text": "至于编次<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">尚书</span>则较简略，没有年月；偶尔有些年月，也多有缺失，不能据以记录。"
    },
    "1.5": {
      "title": "疑则传疑",
      "text": "所以凡是有疑问的就作为疑问流传下来，这大概是慎重的缘故。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "作三代世表缘由",
      "text": ""
    },
    "2.1": {
      "title": "谍记有年数",
      "text": "我读过谱谍一类的记载，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>以来都有年数。"
    },
    "2.2": {
      "title": "历谱乖异",
      "text": "考察那些历谱谱牒所记的始终和<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">五德之传</span>，古书都不相同，彼此乖违差异。"
    },
    "2.3": {
      "title": "孔子不论年月",
      "text": "夫子不编次三代年月，难道是无缘无故的吗！"
    },
    "2.4": {
      "title": "作世表",
      "text": "于是我根据<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">五帝系谍</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">尚书</span>，汇集从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>以来直到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">共和</span>的世系，作成世表。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "张夫子问",
      "text": ""
    },
    "3.1": {
      "title": "契稷无父而生之疑",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张夫子</span>问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">褚先生</span>说： \"<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>中说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>都无父而生。现在考察诸传记都说他们有父亲，而父亲都是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>的子孙，岂不是与<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>相矛盾吗？\""
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "褚先生答",
      "text": ""
    },
    "4.1": {
      "title": "卵生与履迹",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">褚先生</span>说： \"不是这样的。<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>生于<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">卵</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>因其母踩人<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">迹</span>而生，是想表明他们有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天命</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">精诚</span>的意思罢了。"
    },
    "4.2": {
      "title": "须人而生",
      "text": "<span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">鬼神</span>不能自己成形，必须借人而生，怎能无父而生呢！一说有父，一说无父，可信的就当作可信来传，可疑的就当作可疑来传，所以两种说法并存。"
    },
    "4.3": {
      "title": "尧封契",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>知道<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">稷</span>都是贤人，是上天所生的，所以封<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十里</span>的封地，其后历经<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀世</span>到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>，成为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之王。"
    },
    "4.4": {
      "title": "尧封后稷",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>知道<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>后世必为王，所以加封他<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百里</span>的封地，其后经过<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千岁</span>，到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文王</span>而有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "契之由来",
      "text": ""
    },
    "5.1": {
      "title": "吞卵生契",
      "text": "<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">诗传</span>说：'<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>的先祖是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>，无父而生。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>的母亲和姐妹在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">玄丘</span>水中沐浴，有<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">燕</span>衔着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">卵</span>掉下来，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>的母亲得到它，就含在口中，不小心吞了下去，于是生下<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>。"
    },
    "5.2": {
      "title": "尧立契为司徒",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>生来贤能，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司徒</span>，赐姓为<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">子氏</span>。子就是兹；兹，就是日益壮大的意思。"
    },
    "5.3": {
      "title": "诗人美颂",
      "text": "<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>人赞美而歌颂说：'<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的社稷广大，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天命</span><span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">玄鸟</span>降下而生<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">商</span>'。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">商</span>是本质，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>是它的号。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "后稷之由来",
      "text": ""
    },
    "6.1": {
      "title": "后稷无父而生",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文王</span>的先祖是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>也是无父而生的。"
    },
    "6.2": {
      "title": "姜嫄履迹",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>的母亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">姜嫄</span>，外出见到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大人</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">迹</span>印而踩了上去，觉得有了身孕，就生下<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>。"
    },
    "6.3": {
      "title": "弃于道中",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">姜嫄</span>以为是无父之子，觉得贱就把他丢弃在道中，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">羊</span>都避开不踩踏他。"
    },
    "6.4": {
      "title": "弃于山泽",
      "text": "又把他抱到山中，山里的人养育他。再把他丢弃在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大泽</span>里，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸟</span>用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">席</span>覆盖他并喂养他。"
    },
    "6.5": {
      "title": "姜嫄收养",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">姜嫄</span>觉得奇怪，因此知道他是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>，于是把他接回抚养长大。"
    },
    "6.6": {
      "title": "尧立为大农",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>知道他有贤才，立他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大农</span>，赐姓为<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">姬氏</span>。姬就是本的意思。"
    },
    "6.7": {
      "title": "诗人颂后稷",
      "text": "<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>人赞美而歌颂说'厥初生民'，这就是深切地加以修治和成就，而说的正是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>的起源。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "孔子论天命",
      "text": ""
    },
    "7.1": {
      "title": "孔子语",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>说：'从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>为<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">子氏</span>，是为了有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>；命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>为<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">姬氏</span>，是为了有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文王</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大王</span>命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">季历</span>，是彰明天降的祥瑞。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太伯</span>逃奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>，于是延续了王业的源头。'"
    },
    "7.2": {
      "title": "天命难言",
      "text": "<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天命</span>难以言说，非<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">圣人</span>莫能见。"
    },
    "7.3": {
      "title": "舜禹契稷皆黄帝子孙",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>都是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>。"
    },
    "7.4": {
      "title": "天报有德",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>谋划<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天命</span>以治<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>泽深及后世，所以他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>都再度<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>，这是上天回报有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>的人。"
    },
    "7.5": {
      "title": "布衣不可王天下",
      "text": "人们不知道这些，以为都是从<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">布衣</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">匹夫</span>兴起的。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">布衣</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">匹夫</span>怎能无缘无故地起而王有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>呢？他们是有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天命</span>如此。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "黄帝后世王天下",
      "text": ""
    },
    "8.1": {
      "title": "问黄帝后世",
      "text": "\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>的后世为什么王有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>如此久远呢？\""
    },
    "8.2": {
      "title": "为民赎命者帝",
      "text": "回答说：\"相传<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君王</span>能为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">万夫</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份·规范：黔首\">百姓（黔首）</span>请求赎命者成为帝，有福荫<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万世</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>就是这样。"
    },
    "8.3": {
      "title": "五政明者王",
      "text": "五政分明，就修<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">礼义</span>；依天时出兵征伐而得利的成为王，有福荫<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千世</span>。"
    },
    "8.4": {
      "title": "蜀王为黄帝后",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>王，也是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>的后代，至今还在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西南</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千里</span>之外，常来朝见归降，向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝进贡，这不正是因为他们祖先有<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>，泽流后世吗？"
    },
    "8.5": {
      "title": "行道德不可忽",
      "text": "推行<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">道德</span>岂可以忽略呢！<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人君</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王者</span>应该举以为鉴。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "霍光之事",
      "text": ""
    },
    "9.1": {
      "title": "霍光亦黄帝后",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">霍子孟</span>名<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">光</span>的，也是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>的后代。"
    },
    "9.2": {
      "title": "博闻者可言",
      "text": "这话可以对博闻远见的人说，却难以对见闻浅薄的人说。凭什么这么说呢？"
    },
    "9.3": {
      "title": "霍者国名",
      "text": "古代<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>以国名为姓。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">霍</span>，是国名。"
    },
    "9.4": {
      "title": "叔处封霍",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>封弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔处</span>于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">霍</span>，后世<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋献公</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">霍</span>公，其后代沦为庶民，往来居住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平阳</span>。"
    },
    "9.5": {
      "title": "平阳属卫",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平阳</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河东</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河东</span>本是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国之地，后分属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>国。"
    },
    "9.6": {
      "title": "以诗言周起后稷",
      "text": "以<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍·规范：诗\">诗经（诗）</span>而言，也可说是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>的后世。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>起于<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>是无父而生的。"
    },
    "9.7": {
      "title": "后稷有父高辛",
      "text": "以<span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">三代</span>世传而言，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>有父亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高辛</span>；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高辛</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>的曾孙。"
    },
    "9.8": {
      "title": "终始传应验",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>的<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">终始传</span>说：'<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兴起<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百有馀年</span>后，将有一人不高不矮，出自<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>地乡里，掌握<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之政，当时有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">婴兒主</span>，想要乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>。'"
    },
    "9.9": {
      "title": "应在霍光",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">霍</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>本来就住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平阳</span>的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>地。我任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎</span>官时，与<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">方士</span>考核功绩在<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">旗亭</span>下相遇，他对我说了这番话。真是不凡啊！"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高辛</span>的后裔，大启祯祥。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">脩己</span>吞食<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">薏</span>苡，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">石纽</span>兴起王业。 <span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天命</span>降<span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">玄鸟</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">简狄</span>生<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">商</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">姜嫄</span>踏<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">迹</span>，福祚流及<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">岐昌</span>。 都承受天数，互有兴亡。 流风所及为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周召</span>，刑罚废置为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成康</span>。 自<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彘</span>之变以后，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>日益强盛。"
    }
  }
}